{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-all-timeline-js","path":"/2015/02/02/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"awesomeListRepo":"karlhorky/learn-to-program","categoryHTML":"","itemHTML":"<h4>Foundation in Web Development</h4>\n<p>The Internet is filled with an ever-expanding number of courses, books and guides for programmers of all skill levels to improve their skills. Unfortunately, these resources are either hard to find or of low quality.</p>\n<p>This list aims to be a curated set of high quality educational resources. The availability of free content on the platform is highlighted along with the primary topics covered.</p>","updatedAt":"2015-02-02T22:11:59.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"h4cc/awesome-elixir","categoryHTML":"<h2>Books</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://pragprog.com/book/cmelixir/metaprogramming-elixir\">Metaprogramming Elixir: Write Less Code, Get More Done (and Have Fun!)</a> - Thorough explanation on how to exploit Elixir's metaprogramming capabilities to improve your Elixir coding by Chris McCord (2015).</li>","updatedAt":"2015-02-02T19:26:51.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"markets/awesome-ruby","categoryHTML":"<h2>Profiler and Optimization</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/evanphx/benchmark-ips\">benchmark-ips</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/evanphx/benchmark-ips\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.5k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCoun